    "body": "Hi @StefanelStan. The last step should be <code>safeTransferFrom(__accounts[0]__, accounts[2], tokenId, { from: accounts[1]})</code>. This is because `accounts[0]` is the actual owner of `tokenId`, as required by the function. See the [docs for this function](https://openzeppelin.org/api/docs/token_ERC721_ERC721.html#safeTransferFrom):\r\n\r\n> `from` - current owner of the token",
